    "long_instructions": "### Create Version 3\r\n\r\n**First, organize your workspace:**\r\n- Move the `play random` block with both backtracks off to the side.\r\n\r\n**Then, code Version 3**:\r\n- Create a third looping backtrack for your GIF. \r\n- When you have something you like, take that code and add it inside the play random block. \r\n- Connect the `play random` block with all three sets of backtracks back under `when run`. \r\n- Create a third trigger with a new sound effect to go with your new backtrack. \r\n- Press \"Run\" and practice triggering your sound effect based on which backtrack was chosen. ",
